* style
`--comment` 
-> 
`-- comment`

* style
`func"qwe"`
->
`func("qwe")`

* style
`func[[qwe]]`
->
`func([[qwe]])`

* style
align function call chain
```lua
something:qq() --
:ww() --
:ee() --
:rr()
```
->
```lua
something:qq() --
         :ww() --
         :ee() --
         :rr()
```

* style
align comments (readly need it?)
```lua 
x = {
    a, -- value a   
    bbb, -- value bbb
    ccccc, -- value ccccc
    function(...) -- value func
        call(...)
    end,
    ddd, -- value ddd
}
```
->
```lua 
x = {
    a,            -- value a   
    bbb,          -- value bbb
    ccccc,        -- value ccccc
    function(...) -- value func
        call(...)
    end,
    ddd,          -- value ddd
}
```